{"tid":751103,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)屍樂園 福爾摩斯1-2","createTime":"2018-07-21T14:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T18:57:42.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"107f98fa7f808eb3c79ca6dd9be5f0be06633b61","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8bdf45eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1de00872\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=70db13ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/Zombieland-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FZombieland-poster.jpg&h=f0f6fdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/236x/16/f3/97/16f397c1a761ea277f83db6f1063e45b--martin-freeman-martin-omalley.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F236x%2F16%2Ff3%2F97%2F16f397c1a761ea277f83db6f1063e45b--martin-freeman-martin-omalley.jpg&h=277f9f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.未來某天，災難降臨世間，天災人禍讓地球瀕臨愛情重傷。更為可怕的是，恐怖病毒肆意蔓延，人類相繼化身為喪失人性、嗜血如命的恐怖殭屍。並且隨著時光的流逝，殭屍的智商不斷提升，已經成為規模龐大的恐怖大軍。經過幾個月的廝殺，居住在德州某小鎮的哥倫布（傑斯&middot;艾森伯格 Jesse Eisenberg 飾）是少數的倖存者之一，他唯唯諾諾，行事謹慎，卻憑著總結出來的經驗一次又一次逃出生天。某天，哥倫布遇見作風驃悍的塔拉哈西（伍迪&middot;哈里遜 Woody Harrelson 飾），兩人一路同行，繼而邂逅性感美艷的姐妹花薇奇塔（艾瑪&middot;史東 Emma Stone 飾）和小石頭（阿比蓋爾&middot;布萊斯林 Abigail Breslin 飾），他們由此開始了一段妙趣橫生、驚險刺激的旅程&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.夏洛克&middot;福爾摩斯、約翰&middot;華生醫生與雷斯崔德探長正在趕去某處，福爾摩斯與華生到達大英博物館的地下室後，發現布萊克伍德勛爵在舉行某種黑魔法儀式，並正嘗試殺掉一名少女作祭品。福爾摩斯和華生成功阻止儀式後，拯救了該少女，而雷斯崔德則於此時到達，並逮捕了布萊克伍德。三個月後，布萊克伍德終於被判絞刑，在監牢，布萊克伍德勛爵利用黑魔法謠言，令警衛及監犯人心惶惶。他要求見福爾摩斯一面。<br />\n這段時間，福爾摩斯已無聊得發慌，甚至嘗試在家發明槍械消音管，而華生則因希望與瑪麗結婚正在準備搬家。華生邀請福爾摩斯與他及瑪莉一同到餐廳晚餐，但進餐前，福爾摩斯卻對瑪麗相當無禮，令瑪麗與華生丟下福爾摩斯離去。晚餐後，福爾摩斯到酒吧拳擊場打拳擊，卻看到了他死對頭之一兼暗戀對象&mdash;&mdash;艾琳&middot;安德勒的身影.....<br />\n<br />\n3.1891年，歐洲已被黑暗籠罩，法國與德國因爲發生的一系列由無政府主義者策劃的爆炸案而處於戰爭戒備狀態。在倫敦，艾琳&middot;艾德勒在跳蚤市場從不明人士手中接獲一個炸彈包裹後把它轉交給了拍賣行裏的一個叫霍夫曼斯塔的醫生，但夏洛克&middot;福爾摩斯及時出現而化解了炸彈襲擊，也從艾琳的手中得到一封神秘信件，但當他出去時卻發現霍夫曼斯塔早已死在拍賣行的旁邊....<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6e0e08e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d837725a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fcc494f46014eef7045baa3b8de23d9df3ee97","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39713592d11f109d98cf43bf0e64cb475635a3ed","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e2cc73ea014be2ec97862b1ef41bff23ed3eca","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8d167f2f9280d529ad27f88bd61b5763de21f3","tid":751103,"uid":178082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"第一個網張圖係乜動畫"},{"pid":"42c93a15e863f7248c3e0a3066098e752b6c5fad","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd544e573dcfd60fa169d90a110294d05af05dc4","tid":751103,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}